                                   </div>
                               </div>`
                            : `<div class="glass-card p-5 rounded-2xl text-center hover-lift transition-all duration-300">
                                   <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-100 to-surface-200 dark:from-surface-700 dark:to-surface-800 rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
